name: Tezos Playground
description:
Interactive Tezos logo. The most fun you're going to have playing with a NFT Tezos logo.
Controls:
- Change the background with numbers 0-9
- Change the background cube z-axis by moving the mouse up and down
- Lock/unlock cube z-axis with 'z'
- Freely spin the logo by clicking moving the mouse
- Mouse scroll wheel for zooming in and out
- Double click the logo to reset camera view
